Program: The Reith Lectures
Title: The Burden of Underdevelopment
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00h4n6g
Last Broadcast Date: Wed 28 Nov 1979
Professor of Political Science at the University of Michigan, Ali Mazrui, considers Africa's lack of economic development in his fourth Reith lecture from his series entitled 'The African Condition'. In this lecture entitled 'The Burden of Underdevelopment', Professor Ali Mazrui questions how such a resource rich region of the world accommodates some of the poorest countries in the world. Show less